10:52.120 --> 10:54.280
being one of the people internally who was pushing

10:54.280 --> 10:57.040
for the Red Hat acquisition, you got to wonder,

10:57.040 --> 10:59.680
maybe this was part of his personal plan for a long time,

10:59.680 --> 11:01.880
and it seems to be working out for him, at least.

