12:34.640 --> 12:36.600
and he has his leadership style.

12:36.600 --> 12:42.200
And I think that he just doesn't want to be in any other position

12:42.200 --> 12:43.200
aside from the top.

12:43.200 --> 12:46.800
So I think that's pretty much what happened here exactly

12:46.800 --> 12:47.640
again.

