21:09.560 --> 21:14.240
that means that he's seen IBM shift in major ways

21:14.240 --> 21:15.520
over the past three decades

21:15.520 --> 21:19.480
from doing mainframes to personal computers

21:19.480 --> 21:22.400
to software services to business consulting

21:22.400 --> 21:25.320
to the cloud and managed services

21:25.320 --> 21:26.440
