22:18.200 --> 22:20.680
IBM runs it somewhat independently,

22:20.680 --> 22:22.400
like a lot of the other business units.

22:22.400 --> 22:23.920
That's why they're business units.

22:23.920 --> 22:26.400
So I would be mildly concerned,

22:26.400 --> 22:28.520
but I'm also more of the wait and see camp

22:28.520 --> 22:29.920
